cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.MM

This paper focuses on multi-object tracking using computer vision techniques, specifically using a neural network approach. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of deep learning techniques, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves the use of end-to-end training, which is a common technique in the field of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the application of the tracking system in Advanced Driver Assistance Systems (ADAS), which suggests that it could belong to cs.RO (Robotics) as well. Finally, the paper involves the use of video data, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.MM (Multimedia).
